The hardest part about this game will be the translation from simple english to
the anglish + manner of speaking. But this isn't the core gameplay.

I need to iterate and play test this thing quickly.

Core gameplay is wiki prompts that disappear and the allows the user to type the
names of hypertext to go to a new wiki prompt. There is an in game timer. Maybe
text comes word by word and disappears when complete. Interrupting can be
seen as rude. Words only stay appeared for like 10 seconds or something like
that. After scolling down to a certain point the text either scrolls up or
restarts at the top. This stuff doesn't matter though; it's just display stuff.

In the play test there are two characters who will fight over some conflict.

